Why are you back so late?

7
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,120
Is it cool?

8
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:56,800
So cool.

9
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,600
It's better than carrying logs.

10
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:04,960
Tomorrow,

11
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,360
I'll beat them all down.

12
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,600
Tomorrow,

13
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,440
I won't be the last one back.

14
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,720
Look at you.

15
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,400
Look at you.

16
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:32,020
I don't want to take the bath anymore.

17
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,320
Stand up.

18
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,820
Let me help you.

19
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:45,920
Come.

20
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,880
Ms. Huo.

21
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:30,620
Who are you?

22
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,680
It's me.

23
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,520
It's you.

24
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,800
When did you come back?

25
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,760
Not long ago.

26
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,440
Where's Xiaojun?

27
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,409
I need to see her.

28
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,440
Over there.

29
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,840
I'll go see her first

30
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,840
and be back later.

31
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:00,440
Xiaojun.

32
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,090
Zhang, here you are.

33
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,080
Who is it?

34
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:17,120
You...why are you dressed like this?

35
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,440
Why are you wearing sunglasses at night?

36
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,920
I don't want to be noticed.

37
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,240
Is it safe these days?

38
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,360
A few days ago, some punks stalked me.

39
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,690
I almost got kidnapped.

40
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:25,800
Stop it.

41
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,600
You must be paranoid.

42
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,560
I'm not.

43
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,800
There are no punks here.

44
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,800
Nobody knows you.

45
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,680
Take your glasses off.

46
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,800
Are you kidding?

47
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,409
I'm a superstar.

48
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,500
Everyone knows me.

49
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,200
You don't believe me?

50
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:44,960
Come and have a look!

51
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,800
Qu Manting is here! Qu Manting is here!

52
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,960
Qu Manting?

53
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,890
No one knows you.

54
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,600
Ridiculous!

55
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,720
Don't people here read the news?

56
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,400
Come on.

57
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,040
People who come here to drink

58
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,240
can barely read.

59
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,240
Even if they could,

60
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,520
they'd all read political news.

61
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,120
Right now,

62
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,760
who has time to read gossips?

63
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,980
Give me some water.

64
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,840
You're a star.

65
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,340
The north is unstable.

66
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,370
Why didn't you stay in Shanghai

67
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,280
but came all the way to Shunyuan?

68
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,210
I have work to do.

69
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,040
My new movie will be filmed here.

70
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,080
It won't be filmed in Shanghai,

71
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,200
but in Shunyuan?

72
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,560
Mr. Shen invested it, right?

73
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,520
No way.

74
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,520
Why not?

75
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,280
He's helped you a lot.

76
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,720
Don't offend him.

77
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,080
What has he done for me?

78
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,400
I'm a star

79
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,400
not a social girl.

80
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,370
What's the difference?

81
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,800
You know what,

82
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,260
you should just marry him.

83
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,520
He's rich and powerful.

84
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,480
He's more than capable to support you.

85
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,400
It's chaotic outside.

86
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:48,960
Listen to me.

87
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,220
It's chaotic outside.

88
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,720
It's dangerous for you

89
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,400
to strive alone.

90
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,760
Enough. Stop it.

91
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,520
My parents almost talked my ears off.

92
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,720
Now you're nagging me, too.

93
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,840
Give me a break.

94
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,000
Then go get married.

95
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:00,760
Look,

96
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,760
you won't have another chance like this.

97
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,440
Listen to me,

98
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,120
Shen Tingbai can't think straight,

99
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,360
so he's attracted to you.

100
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,720
When he comes around one day,

101
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,960
he'll be attracted to another woman.

102
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,720
I must thank her then.

103
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,720
Goodness!

104
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,700
He likes me so I must marry him?

105
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,480
Tons of men also like me.

106
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,320
Besides,

107
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,640
I make a living on my own.

108
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,720
My money is hard-earned.

109
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,760
I can use it as I please.

110
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,090
Why should I rely on him?

111
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,000
Without him,

112
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,520
you think you could sit here now?

113
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,720
You would've been kidnapped at Paramo.

114
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,720
How did you know that?

115
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,520
I...

116
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,120
I... That day, I...

117
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,120
meant to

118
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,720
introduce a friend to you

119
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,400
so I was there.

120
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,640
Why didn't you help me?

121
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,560
Stop blaming me.

122
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,440
I was almost scared to death.

123
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,040
How could I help you?

124
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,080
I couldn't beat him.

125
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:49,840
Also,

126
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,880
if I came to help you,

127
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,760
-how could Mr. Shen... -Go away.

128
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,680
play the hero?

129
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,420
Why are you here today?

130
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,520
Since you work here,

131
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,680
you must've known people at the Academy.

132
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,480
What's wrong?

133
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,400
You know,

134
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,760
I investigated that bastard later on.

135
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,640
He went to the Academy at night.

136
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:13,560
You know how embarrassed I was that day?

137
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,560
He spanked me!

138
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,600
Why are you laughing?

139
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,930
It's embarrassing, OK?

140
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:19,920
If he falls into my hands,

141
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,000
I'll gut him.

142
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,280
You?

143
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,480
I won't do it myself.

144
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,600
Just tell me

145
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,880
when the school break is

146
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,280
and when he'll come home.

147
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,640
Speaking of the Academy,

148
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,720
I do

149
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,600
know someone.

150
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:35,280
You do?

151
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,030
Really?

152
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,080
Who is him?

153
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,909
Do I know him?

154
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:40,120
Is he a teacher or a student?

155
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,720
You...you don't need to know.

156
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,909
I'll help you ask around.

157
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:43,840
What's his name?

158
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,440
Gu Yanzhen.

159
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,600
You were in the well a whole day.

160
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,730
You may catch a cold.

161
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,690
I have medicine.

162
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,440
Here.

163
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,560
Don't talk to me.

164
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,100
I need to calm down.

165
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,400
Whatever.

166
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,220
Will you show up on time tomorrow?

167
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,300
I'm talking to you.

168
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,880
If you're late again,

169
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,340
we'll both be in the water.

170
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,760
We'll see.

171
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,720
My brain is a mess now.

172
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,000
Lunatic.

173
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,160
Like I want to talk to you.

174
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:49,680
Morning.

175
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,240
Hi, morning.

176
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,100
See you in a bit.

177
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,680
Gu Yanzhen.

178
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,200
Wake up.

179
00:09:59,280 --> 00:09:59,960
Get up.

180
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,480
Get up!

181
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,700
It's for your good.

182
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,440
Are you crazy?

183
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:29,960
Go away!

184
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:33,920
Let go.

185
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,960
Let go.

186
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,040
Have you done?

187
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,440
Say it!

188
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,040
Excuse me.

189
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,040
What now?

190
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,120
Let go!

191
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:05,610
You can't go.

192
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:08,960
You can't. You can't.

193
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,730
Watch and learn.

194
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,080
Stop.

195
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,570
You don't have something to do?

196
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,440
Sir, let me go.

197
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,640
Close your mouth.

198
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,560
You're not busy, are you?

199
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:52,920
Sergeant Song.

200
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,640
You have a visitor.

201
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,200
OK.

202
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,610
You two behave yourselves.

203
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,800
Got it?

204
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,200
Yes, sir.

205
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,000
Yes, sir.

206
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:18,700
What are you doing?

207
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,800
Gu Yanzhen.

208
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:26,160
Gu Yanzhen, I'll kill you!

209
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,840
I'm exhausted. I need to rest.

210
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:28,680
Yeah.

211
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,280
They're arguing again.

212
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,120
What's happening?

213
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,960
You're welcome.

214
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,760
Ignore them.

215
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:34,400
They bicker every day.

216
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,560
I'll rip your head off, bastard!

217
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:36,280
They're fighting again?

218
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:36,800
Yeah.

219
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,080
Let go.

220
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,680
They're fighting again?

221
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:52,520
Liangchen,

222
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:55,010
can you stop fighting against Gu Yanzhen?

223
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,760
You can't beat him anyway.

224
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:58,490
You always end up getting hurt.

225
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,680
I don't have a choice.

226
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,960
He's such a bully.

227
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:04,880
Actually,

228
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,280
I think he's not that bad.

229
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,720
Are you blind or what?

230
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,680
He's a thug.

231
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:15,090
Alright.

232
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:16,600
Enough of him.

233
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,600
Our break is in two days.

234
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,600
What's your plan?

235
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,880
I...I'm going to visit my friend.

236
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,080
And you?

237
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,760
I'm going to my sister's.

238
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:27,440
I see.

239
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,810
You said your sister got married here.

240
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,560
My sister and I,

241
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,440
together with my brother,

242
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,240
fled our hometown and came here.

243
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,240
I joined the army.

244
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,480
My sister got married.

245
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,210
My brother is studying in town.

246
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,900
He's in middle school now.

247
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,360
Really?

248
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,090
That's impressive.

249
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:46,000
My brother is the smartest in my family.

250
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,680
When I was young, my dad said

251
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,520
he'd sell anything at home

252
00:15:50,800 --> 00:15:52,400
just so we could go to school.

253
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,250
Winning a scholar title

254
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,120
would bring honor to our family.

255
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,120
Sadly,

256
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,840
there are no such titles now.

257
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,820
Your brother is in middle school.

258
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,770
It's as good as winning that title.

259
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,330
What are you guys doing?

260
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,400
You're welcome.

261
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:15,760
That course is surprisingly interesting.

262
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,890
I'm surprised, too.

263
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:18,200
Xiaojun.

264
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,640
My friend is here.

265
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,520
I gotta go.

266
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,560
Bye-bye.

267
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:24,280
Goodbye.

268
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:25,690
Who is he?

269
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,600
Xiang!

270
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:30,560
It's me!

271
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:31,800
I miss you so much!

272
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:32,720
Let's go.

273
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,440
Let's go.

274
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:35,200
Do you miss me?

275
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:36,600
Of course I do.

276
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:39,720
Who is he?

277
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:43,610
Let's go.

278
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,640
How are you going?

279
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,970
Is your training tough?

280
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,080
Can you handle it?

281
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,280
Who's your roommate?

282
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,370
Has he found out that you're a girl?

283
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,200
Don't mention it.

284
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,440
I don't want to talk about him.

285
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,170
What's wrong? Did he bully you?

286
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,960
We can talk about it later.

287
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:01,960
Here's the thing.

288
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:04,220
I'll stay at your place for a few days.

289
00:17:04,349 --> 00:17:05,280
It's school break.

290
00:17:05,280 --> 00:17:06,829
My classmates have all gone home.

291
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:08,760
I don't want to be in the dorm alone.

292
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,400
The thing is

293
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,119
the fewer people know

294
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:14,400
your secret, the safer you are.

295
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,349
So I don't even tell my parents.

296
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:19,240
It's not appropriate for you to go to my home

297
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:19,960
