307
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:38,360
How are you?

308
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,360
Are you in your break?

309
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,560
You're skinny

310
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,760
and tanned.

311
00:17:45,840 --> 00:17:47,400
I had a lot of schoolwork to do

312
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,360
so I lost some weight.

313
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,520
You're a girl.

314
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,880
You should take good care of yourself.

315
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:53,560
Why don't you stay?

316
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,850
