320
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,080
-Back then, we were... -Mom.

321
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,650
Stop nagging, will you?

322
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,160
Xie Xiang will be staying with us for a while.

323
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,560
We're eating out tonight.

324
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,840
Why are you eating out?

325
