329
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:15,080
A boy or a girl?

330
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:15,680
A girl.

331
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,930
We're leaving, mom.

332
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:18,840
Let's go.

333
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:19,800
See you later.

334
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:20,800
Let's go.

335
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:21,760
Come back early.

336
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,400
My mom can't stop nagging me.

337
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,480
Moms are all the same.

338
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:28,740
You've met my mom, too.

339
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:33,100
Where are we going now?

340
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:34,520
Over there.

341
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:36,040
There's a high-end restaurant.

342
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,370
A high-end restaurant?

343
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,400
Who's paying?

344
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,280
So generous.

345
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,560
You don't need to know.

346
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:43,420
Just follow me.

347
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:50,360
How are you, ladies?

348
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:51,160
How many of you?

349
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:51,720
Hello.

350
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:52,640
Ms. Qu has reserved.

351
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,600
This way, please.

352
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:54,280
Thanks.

353
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:55,740
Xiaojun, here.

354
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:00,480
This way.

355
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,690
Where are you going?

356
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,000
You're late

357
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:08,290
