359
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:11,280
I'm sorry.

360
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:12,240
It's my fault.

361
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:15,650
Won't you introduce us?

362
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:16,480
This is my friend

363
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,080
Xie Xiang.

364
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:17,600
Xie Xiang,

365
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,640
this is Qu Manting,

366
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:20,400
the most famous star in Shanghai,

367
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,260
also my bestie.

368
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,480
Only in Shanghai?

369
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:24,280
I'm famous all over the country.

370
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,600
Xie Xiang, right?

371
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:28,000
I'm Qu Manting.

372
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,760
I'm easy to get along with.

373
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:30,640
Just relax.

374
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,090
