375
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,040
Have a seat. Sit down.

376
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:39,560
Sit.

377
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:47,800
What's wrong?

378
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,000
Look how cocky she is.

379
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:57,640
May I ask,

380
00:19:58,600 --> 00:19:59,880
