381
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,720
You seem familiar to me.

382
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:03,040
Impossible.

383
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,490
We've never met before.

384
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,520
Really?

385
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:08,420
Where are you from?

386
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:09,690
Are you also a local?

387
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:10,720
No.

388
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,240
I'm from Peking.

389
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,760
I've never come to Shunyuan before.

390
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,560
Neither have I been to Shanghai.

391
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,760
I am familiar with your face.

392
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:27,300
But I can't remember where we've met.

393
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:28,760
Just let it go.

394
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:29,480
Order some food now.

395
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,280
I'm starving.

396
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,080
Wait a minute.

397
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,490
There's another guest.

398
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,720
Who is it?

399
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,130
Who else could it be?

400
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,600
Mr. Shen of course.

401
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:39,600
