402
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:49,090
Mr. Shen, this way, please.

403
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,760
What's up now?

404
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,480
That's my classmate.

405
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:08,760
Hello.

406
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:10,130
Manting,

407
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,160
this is my brother

408
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:13,360
Shen Junshan.

409
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:15,260
He just came back from abroad.

410
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:17,320
You were playmates when you were young.

411
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:18,120
Do you remember?

412
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:19,120
Shen Junshan.

413
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,920
I remember.

414
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:23,400
He used to follow you around

415
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,640
