416
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:27,770
You...you've changed dramatically.

417
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,730
You're like a whole new person.

418
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,620
You've changed a lot, too.

419
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:33,920
That night at Paramo,

420
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,240
I didn't even recognize you.

421
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:37,000
Let go!

422
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:38,160
Help me!

423
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,400
Please help me!

424
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:41,400
Help me!

425
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:43,480
I remember it!

426
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:46,250
Why didn't you help me that day?

427
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,240
You haven't introduced her.

428
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:57,810
Manting,

429
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:00,010
why don't you introduce us?

430
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,320
She's Xiaojun's friend.

431
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,160
She's...

432
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:05,130
She's...

433
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,160
I'm sorry. I don't feel well.

434
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:08,160
Please excuse me.

435
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:09,880
I'll go with her.

436
00:22:21,600 --> 00:22:22,660
Let's order first.

437
00:22:23,560 --> 00:22:24,080
Here.

438
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:31,880
Crap, crap, crap!

439
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,640
Shen Junshan is my classmate.

440
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,360
Did I seem odd just now?

441
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,980
He must've recognized me.

442
00:22:37,080 --> 00:22:38,280
I don't think so.

443
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,360
Also,

444
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:41,240
