445
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:44,090
I don't think he can recognize you easily.

446
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,000
Hey you,

447
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:47,400
why didn't you tell me

448
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,520
your celebrity friend would be here?

449
00:22:48,520 --> 00:22:50,000
We met once at Paramo.

450
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:51,920
Last time,

451
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:54,020
I didn't get to introduce you two,

452
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,740
so I accepted her invitation.

453
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,160
So many things happened last time.

454
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,360
She wouldn't remember you.

455
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:59,160
You don't know.

456
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,800
I met her in the ladies' room before her show.

457
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,930
She thought I was a pervert and beat me.

458
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,640
You...you didn't tell me.

459
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,570
How would I know?

460
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:07,760
I'm doomed.

461
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:08,920
He must've recognized me.

462
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,080
What should I do?

463
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,280
Just chill.

464
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:17,760
Don't scare yourself.

465
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,680
Calm down.

466
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:21,520
How about this?

467
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:23,080
You go home first.

468
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:23,480
And

469
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:25,010
I'll go back to talk to them.

470
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,600
Will it work?

471
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,680
It should be OK.

472
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:31,720
I'll tell them you're needed elsewhere.

473
00:23:32,360 --> 00:23:33,760
Then I'll sound them out.

474
00:23:35,280 --> 00:23:36,280
I'm leaving then.

475
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,440
Take a stroll along the street

476
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,760
before you go back to my home.

477
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:41,490
I'll be back as soon as I'm done.

478
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:42,960
Don't be back too late.

479
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,690
Don't worry.

480
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:44,680
Be careful.

481
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:28,690
Stop the car.

482
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,720
Young master, what's wrong?

483
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:44,840
Nothing.

484
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:45,480
Let's go.

485
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,520
Here's the noodles.

486
00:25:12,760 --> 00:25:13,920
Eat it while it's warm.

487
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:14,760
Eat. Come on.

488
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,040
Smells good.

489
00:25:21,360 --> 00:25:22,480
So is Sheng Junshan

490
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,810
really your classmate?

491
00:25:25,320 --> 00:25:25,880
He is.

492
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,080
You're so lucky.

493
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,520
Shen Junshan is well-educated and handsome.

494
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:32,320
I heard he came back from abroad.

495
00:25:32,760 --> 00:25:34,290
If I could see him every day,

496
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,730
I'd be willing to be a man

497
00:25:35,840 --> 00:25:37,400
