498
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:38,400
Enough.

499
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:40,680
I was almost scared to death.

500
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:41,920
Luckily, they didn't recognize me.

501
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:42,680
Relax.

502
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,800
I've observed them for you.

503
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:44,930
Your secret is safe.

504
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,800
You should see his stern face.

505
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,060
What is he like?

506
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:53,000
Is he super elegant and attractive?

507
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,000
A real gentleman?

508
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:55,960
You're helpless!

509
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:58,200
Tell me about it.

510
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,000
Stop eating.

511
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,570
He's good-looking.

512
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,960
What does his family do?

513
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:12,760
His family seems powerful.

514
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:13,820
Rich and powerful.

515
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:15,440
Shen is a household name.

516
00:26:15,840 --> 00:26:18,680
Shen Tingbai is the chairman of the Chamber of Commerce.

517
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,960
In Shunyuan,

518
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,480
