519
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,610
and well connected.

520
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,760
The Shens and the Qus have been friends for long.

521
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:27,360
Mr. Shen's loved Qu Manting since he was young.

522
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:29,620
Well, I don't get to see him too often.

523
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:38,000
Xiang,

524
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,360
I know from my dad

525
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:42,520
the news these days are all about

526
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,400
battles all over the country

527
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,360
and casualties.

528
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:45,840
It's scary.

529
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:48,240
You're a student at the Military Academy.

530
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,400
Will you be sent to the battlefield someday?

531
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,930
Aren't you afraid as a girl?

532
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:57,820
If your brother were still alive,

533
00:26:58,080 --> 00:27:00,140
he wouldn't want to see you like this.

534
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:28,940
What are you doing?

535
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:30,620
Someone sent us

536
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,200
to teach you a lesson.

537
00:27:37,320 --> 00:27:38,440
Someone sent you.

538
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,640
How much did they pay you?

539
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:42,280
I'm rich.

540
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,520
I can pay you more.

541
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:44,600
Sorry, sir.

542
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:45,640
I can't do this.

543
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:47,800
We have rules.

544
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:49,280
I'm afraid

545
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,740
I can't help you today.

546
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:51,880
Do it.

547
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,410
Wait, wait a second.

548
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,200
Before you hit me,

549
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:57,280
can...

550
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:59,440
can you at least tell me who I offended

551
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:01,040
so that I could rest in peace?

552
00:28:01,760 --> 00:28:03,160
The one you offended

553
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:05,040
is a powerful figure.

554
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:07,160
Shut up.

555
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,400
What's wrong with you?

556
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,320
How many times have I told you

557
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,340
