558
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:15,120
Don't you know the rules?

559
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:21,300
You don't need to ask them.

560
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,600
I sent them here.

561
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,280
