563
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,360
Had I known it was you,

564
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:30,490
I wouldn't have struggled so hard.

565
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:31,930
What do you mean?

566
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:36,800
Do it.

567
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,000
Run!

568
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,300
Hey pretty,

569
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,920
don't you know

570
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:58,000
it's dangerous

571
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:00,060
