572
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,660
in the street at night?

573
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,360
Why are you so close to me?

574
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:04,290
Get away from me.

575
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,810
Aren't you trying to

576
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:07,840
