577
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,480
I'm right here.

578
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:10,960
Go ahead.

579
00:29:14,080 --> 00:29:15,480
Why don't we call it a day?

580
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,380
Let's meet some other day.

581
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,280
OK. Sure.

582
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,080
Some other day?

583
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:22,160
If I let you go,

584
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:23,760
